    "## One-Step Reachability and Graph Representations\n",
    "\n",
    "What are conceivable operations on graphs?  There are some basic ones, such as adding a vertex and adding an edge.  These are easily taken care of."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "id": "f6908d19",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "TJA5XYRDhLoj",
